%% Ciclo de vida de una reserva
%% Dominio: booking | Tipo: state
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending: Reserva creada

    pending --> confirmed: Pago exitoso
    pending --> cancelled: Timeout / cancelación

    confirmed --> inProgress: Inicio del servicio
    confirmed --> cancelled: Cancelación con reembolso

    inProgress --> completed: Servicio finalizado
    inProgress --> disputed: Reclamo abierto

    completed --> [*]
    disputed --> resolved: Resolución
    resolved --> [*]
    cancelled --> [*]
